Robert Carter III

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Robert Carter III





Born
February 1727/28


Died
March 10, 1804(1804-03-10)


Nationality
American


Alma mater
College of William and Mary


Occupation
planter


Known for
manumission


Spouse(s)
